18 12:00:00','no',NULL),(37,4,'Desired in the 3 Worlds','516475439','http://rawtapes.bandcamp.com/album/the-guadaloop-in-desired-in-the-3-worlds','','<p>\n	This 25 tracks album is all based on Indian/Bollywood samples from vinyls The Guadaloop bought back in 2007. Back then, after being inspired by his good friend Plusga, Guada(Loop) went to the nearest record store and got all the Indian records he could find. Soon Guada linked up with a big vinyl dealer and brought dozens of Indian\\African records to the studio. loads of beats were made from this vinyls in the past 3 years &ndash; most of them haven&rsquo;t been published yet. Some tracks on the LP were made in 2007 and some 2 days before the release date (Plusga &ndash; Penny Fuck) The name for the LP &ndash; &ldquo;Desired in the 3 Worlds&rdquo; comes from the Sanskrit/Hindi word - &ldquo;Trilok Kamaya&rdquo; &ndash; or in another words - &ldquo;Leaf of Heroes&rdquo; &ndash; or in another words - &ldquo;Conqueror of the 3 regions of the universe&rdquo; &ndash; or in another words - &ldquo;The Green One&rdquo;&hellip; Ganja.</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#696969;\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;\">All Tracks Produced and Mixed By The Guadaloop @ Raw Tapes Studio</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#696969;\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;\">*Except - Tracks 5, 14, 21, 24 &ndash; Produced and Mixed By Plusga</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#696969;\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;\">Track 15 &ndash; Produced and Mixed By Rejoicer</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#696969;\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;\">Art by Jengo</span></span></p>\n','d54e0-desired.jpg','2010-09-19 12:00:00','desired',NULL),(38,2,'Tales From The Chimney','3325817430','http://rawtapes.bandcamp.com/album/tales-from-the-chimney','','<p>\n	Mo Rayon on the raps, Mesh on the cuts, Beno on the production and Nomok with the synths! Enjoy this hazy christmas production!</p>\n<p>\n	HO ho HO</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"color